query: SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT m.Nickname), m.Joined FROM Championship AS m GROUP BY m.Joined
question: How many unique nicknames of institutions joined in each year?

query: SELECT n.Nickname FROM Championship AS n WHERE n.Number_of_Championships BETWEEN 1 AND 10 ORDER BY n.Nickname ASC
question: What are the nicknames of institutions that have won between 1 and 10 championships, listed in ascending order by nickname?

query: SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT Stadium), Enrollment FROM Championship JOIN institution ON Championship.Institution_ID = institution.Institution_ID
question: What is the number of unique stadiums and the enrollment of institutions that have won championships?

query: SELECT Nickname FROM Championship WHERE Institution_ID > 82 ORDER BY Nickname ASC;
question: What are the nicknames of the institutions with an institution id greater than 82, listed in alphabetical order?

query: SELECT SUM(Capacity), Enrollment FROM institution WHERE Enrollment BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND EXISTS (SELECT * FROM Championship WHERE  Number_of_Championships >= 73 AND institution.Institution_ID = Championship.Institution_ID) ORDER BY Enrollment DESC
question: What is the sum of stadium capacities and the enrollment of institutions with between 1 and 10 enrolled students, and have won at least 73 championships, listed in descending order of enrollment?

query: SELECT Enrollment FROM Championship JOIN institution ON Championship.Institution_ID = institution.Institution_ID WHERE Joined BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND  Championship.Institution_ID < 85
question: What is the enrollment of institutions with institution ids less than 85 that joined between 1 and 10 championships?

query: SELECT AVG(c.Joined) AS Joined_Avg, COUNT(DISTINCT c.Nickname), c.Nickname, c.Number_of_Championships FROM Championship AS c WHERE c.Institution_ID BETWEEN 1 AND 10 GROUP BY c.Number_of_Championships, c.Nickname HAVING COUNT(c.Number_of_Championships) < 33 ORDER BY c.Number_of_Championships DESC
question: What is the average year that institutions with fewer than 33 championships joined, along with the number of distinct nicknames, for institutions with IDs between 1 and 10, grouped by the number of championships and nickname, and sorted in descending order by the number of championships?

query: SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT Team), Province, Affiliation FROM institution WHERE Capacity >= 67 GROUP BY Province, Affiliation ORDER BY Province ASC;
question: What is the number of distinct teams in each province and affiliation for institutions with a capacity of at least 67, listed in ascending order by province?

query: SELECT Founded FROM institution WHERE Capacity BETWEEN 1 AND 10 AND Name IN (SELECT Name FROM institution AS v WHERE v.Founded BETWEEN 1 AND 10 LIMIT 10) ORDER BY Founded DESC LIMIT 9
question: What are the next 1 earliest founding years of institutions with a capacity between 1 and 10 among the top 10 earliest founding years of all institutions with a capacity between 1 and 10?

query: SELECT Name, Province FROM Championship JOIN institution ON Championship.Institution_ID = institution.Institution_ID WHERE  institution.Institution_ID < 7 ORDER BY Province DESC LIMIT 8
question: What are the names of institutions and their provinces for the institutions with an institution id less than 7, listed in descending order of province, starting from the 9th result?

query: SELECT Name, Enrollment FROM institution WHERE City IN (SELECT City FROM institution AS q WHERE  q.Institution_ID <= 41) GROUP BY Name, Enrollment HAVING Enrollment >= 6
question: What are the names and enrollments of institutions located in cities where at least one institution has an id of 41 or less and the enrollment is 6 or more?

query: SELECT n.Enrollment FROM institution AS n
question: What is the enrollment of the institution?

query: SELECT Institution_ID FROM institution WHERE  Capacity < 79 AND EXISTS (SELECT * FROM Championship AS z WHERE institution.Institution_ID = z.Institution_ID)
question: What are the institution ids of institutions with a stadium capacity of less than 79 that have won championships?

query: SELECT Joined, Institution_ID FROM Championship WHERE  Joined < 46 ORDER BY Joined DESC LIMIT 1
question: What is the institution id of the second most recent institution to join with the number of years since joining being more than 45?

query: SELECT Number_of_Championships FROM Championship WHERE  Institution_ID < 28 ORDER BY Number_of_Championships DESC
question: What are the number of championships for institutions with id less than 28, listed in order of most championships to least?

query: SELECT c1.Institution_ID, c2.Number_of_Championships FROM Championship AS c1 JOIN Championship AS c2 ON c1.Institution_ID = c2.Institution_ID WHERE c1.Joined < 2021 GROUP BY c2.Number_of_Championships LIMIT 1;
question: Which institution that joined before 2021 has the least number of championships?

query: SELECT MIN(a.Enrollment), a.Name FROM institution AS a
question: What is the smallest enrollment and the name of the institution with that enrollment?

query: SELECT AVG(T1.Number_of_Championships), T1.Nickname FROM Championship AS T1 JOIN institution AS T2 ON T1.Institution_ID = T2.Institution_ID WHERE T1.Joined > 61 AND T2.Institution_ID > (SELECT MAX(Institution_ID) FROM institution WHERE Institution_ID < 53)
question: What is the average number of championships won and the nickname of institutions with an institution ID greater than the maximum institution ID less than 53 and that joined after 61 years?

query: SELECT AVG(Enrollment) AS avg_enrollment, Endowment FROM institution WHERE Founded BETWEEN 1 AND 10 GROUP BY Endowment
question: What is the average enrollment and endowment for institutions founded between 1 and 10 years ago, grouped by endowment?

query: SELECT COUNT(i.Founded), i.Stadium, i.City FROM institution AS i WHERE i.Name = (SELECT MAX(Name) FROM institution) GROUP BY i.City, i.Stadium ORDER BY i.City DESC;
question: For institutions with the maximum name, what is the count of their founding year, grouped by city and stadium, ordered by city in descending order?

query: SELECT MIN(h.Capacity), AVG(h.Enrollment) FROM institution AS h;
question: What is the smallest stadium capacity and average enrollment of institutions?

query: SELECT AVG(k.Capacity) FROM institution AS k WHERE  k.Enrollment != 14 LIMIT 7
question: What are the average capacities of the next 7 institutions with an enrollment other than 14, after the first 7, when ordered by capacity?

query: SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT v.Nickname), v.Number_of_Championships FROM Championship AS v WHERE Number_of_Championships IN (SELECT Number_of_Championships FROM Championship AS i) GROUP BY v.Number_of_Championships;
question: What are the counts of distinct nicknames for each number of championships?

query: SELECT f.Joined, f.Nickname FROM Championship AS f WHERE  f.Joined <= 62 ORDER BY f.Nickname DESC
question: What are the nicknames and corresponding joining years of institutions that joined championship 62 years ago or earlier, listed in descending order by nickname?

query: SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT Institution_ID) FROM Championship WHERE Institution_ID NOT IN (SELECT Institution_ID FROM institution AS s WHERE  s.Enrollment < 94)
question: How many institutions with an enrollment of 94 or more have won championships?

query: SELECT c1.Nickname FROM Championship AS c1 JOIN Championship AS c2 ON c2.Institution_ID = c1.Institution_ID ORDER BY c1.Nickname DESC;
question: What are the nicknames of institutions that have won championships, listed in descending order?

query: SELECT Nickname FROM Championship WHERE  Joined >= 69
question: What are the nicknames of the institutions that joined the championship in 1969 or later?
